producer_info_data: Järgnev on toores JSON mille plokitootja esitas plokiahelale.

producer_json_unavailable_content: See plokitootja ei ole veel avaldanud oma kandideerimisteavet "producerjson" tarka lepingusse EOS plokiahelas.
producers_no_voting: Block producers are not voted in on this Blockchain, therefore this section is read-only
producer_vote_description: Vote to support this candidate as a rewarded block producer on the {{chainSymbol}} network.
producer_voter_no_producers_votes_cast_s: Iga konto võib hääletada kuni 30 kandidaadi poolt. Kasuta paremal pool olevat tabelit et valida ja hääletada enda poolt valitud plokitootajte poolt.
producer_voter_preview_confirm_changes_m: Selle toiminguga seatakse sinu valitud plokitootjad järgnevalt.
producer_voter_preview_transaction_succe: Toiming on salvestatud plokiahelasse. Tehingu teavet võid leida allpoolt.
producer_voter_remove_all_votes_subheade: Salvestamine, peale kõikide häälte eemaldamist, eemaldab eelnevalt antud hääled kõikidelt tootjatelt.
producers_form_proxy_confirming_change_t: See toiming seab sinu häälte volituse
All producer votes cast by the proxy above will now gain the benefit and weight of this accounts staked {{chainSymbol}}. You will no longer be able to cast votes on your own.
producers_form_proxy_confirming_remove_t: sinu volitatud hääletajana. Hiljem saad uuesti hääletada või määrata uue volitatud hääletaja.
producers_form_proxy_label: Sisesta konto nimi, keda soovite volitada oma häälte kaalu kasutamaks tootja valimisel
producers_form_proxy_message: If you do not have the time to research Block Producers on a regular basis, proxying your votes to a trustworthy proxy voter can be a very good way to use your voting power efficiently. Simply enter an account name or browse through the list of registered proxy voters to proxy your votes. This can be revoked at any time.
producers_proxies_popup_content: Click on this button to change your proxy voter to {{proxy}}.

producers_warning_have_unregistered_mult: The block producers ({{unregisteredBps}}) will be automatically removed from your selection as they are now unregistered.
producers_warning_have_unregistered_sing: The block producer ({{unregisteredBp}}) will be automatically removed from your selection as they are now unregistered.
